summary: An Ordinance providing for the laying-off, extending, widening and establishing of California Avenue, from West Webster Street to Upper Court, and of West Webster Street, from California Avenue to Forty-fourth Avenue Southwest; providing for the condemnation, appropriation, taking and damaging of land and other property necessary therefor; and providing that the entire cost of said improvement shall be paid by special assessment upon property specially benefited, in the manner provided by law.
